         <div type="translation" resp="part:vito">
             <p>Hommage to the Bhagavant, the Buddha! … a pillar and two floor slabs (?) were ordered to be made, by Saṅgha-…, <supplied reason="subaudible">and</supplied> Mahāsenadatta—the Sa(ṁ)tika …</p>
